ext":"三天不读毛主席的书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思想掉队心糊涂。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"早晨读了毛主席的书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"精神焕发干劲足。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晚上读了毛主席的书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"半夜三更红日出。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"天天都读毛主席的书，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"干革命永远不迷路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王树品"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜读"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜已深，未入眠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作展眼前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越学精神越振奋，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命干劲浑身添。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"夜已深，未入眠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席话儿涌心间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越思越想心越明，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远做个战斗员。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"徐耕农"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作学得好，千斤重担也敢挑。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小组会上抓思想，革命红旗举得高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一轮红日书中出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士能文又能武，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"练武更爱读“红书”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“红书”本是哪位著？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当代巨人毛泽东！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读得青山探过头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苍松翠柏齐招手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读得大海凝神听，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"惊涛骇浪也驯服。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捧着“红书”飞云间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阴霾恶雾让开路。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"捧着“红书”浪里走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"险滩逆流难挡阻。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对着东海读“红书”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一轮红日书中出，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怀藏“红书”干革命，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心红眼亮不迷途！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈荣"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"读《关于重庆谈判》随感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"艰苦环境长志气，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"困难有啥了不起！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席教导记心中，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越干浑身越有力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杨庆光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人磨刀我磨刀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——读《丢掉幻想，准备斗争》有感"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席教导记得牢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人磨刀我磨刀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"严寒酷暑有何惧，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二百米硬功定学到。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席教导记得牢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敌人磨刀我磨刀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"擦亮眼睛握紧枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远站在最前哨。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"郑世骥"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光照在我身上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我是一株嫩苗苗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“毛著”是轮红太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光照在我身上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"开花结果长得强。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“红九连”副班长 张文奎"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"行军一条龙，休息一片红。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚决学习白求恩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白求恩，外国人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来咱中国当医生。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"上火线，救伤员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共产主义好精神。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自己应该怎么办？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坚决学习白求恩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"薛世福"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙腾虎跃飞上天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳月亮忙替换，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟我行军八九天；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越过九十九道河，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"翻过九十九座山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"累得月亮歪半边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"困得太阳不露脸。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士腰疼腿又酸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哟，前面又是一座山！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"悬崖陡壁把路拦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声号令向下传："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原地休息十分钟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"准备火把向上攀。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根火把一堆人，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人人围着读“毛选”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手捧“毛选”力量增，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"龙腾虎跃飞上天！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王树品"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱支“花儿”颂“毛著”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鸡叫三遍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一遍比一遍亮哩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路走三遍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一遍比一遍熟哩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作暖人心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千遍万遍地读哩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"松柏常青，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四季都不变色哩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"保卫祖国，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"满腔热血一身胆哩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作象太阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照得心窝里暖哩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刺刀闪光，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"杀声震天地喊哩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士练武，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身的劲用不完哩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作是动力，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"带着我们朝共产主义奔哩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"边明德"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"颂毛主席语录板"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"语录板，不简单，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席教导在上边，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"句句叫咱快步走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"字字催咱永向前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看一遍，想十遍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身力气用不完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要问威力有多大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"赛过特大原子弹。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“红九连”战士 陈昌玉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"学好“毛著”力量大，天大的困难踩脚下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千锁万锁脚下落"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个困难一把锁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个问题一把锁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一件工作一把锁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"思想疙瘩也是锁。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千把锁，万把锁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难把革命战士锁；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用上“毛著”金钥匙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千锁万锁脚下落！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张宗田"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就象在毛主席身边"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又隔水，又隔山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席跟我把话谈，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是毛主席来营房，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是他的著作在眼前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看一遍，想一遍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越学胸怀越觉宽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就象毛主席身边坐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"句句话儿暖心间。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"韦汉伦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宝中宝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席著作宝中宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命人民不能少。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辨别是非明方向，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"永远不会走歪道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横扫一切害人精，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"牛鬼蛇神全铲掉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"工人有了这个宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"勤俭建国记得牢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奋发图强立壮志，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"自力更生办法高。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"比学赶帮争上游，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动干劲冲云霄。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"农民有了这个宝，"